OL,4,Clife-threatening heart condition
OL,6,FA Nottinghamshire artist who lives
OL,7,Fwith the same life-threatening heart
OL,8,Fcondition that took her mother's life
OL,9,Fheld a silent auction of her work to
OL,10,Fraise funds for the British Heart
OL,11,FFoundation.
OL,13,FRenee Mascari from Ruddington lives
OL,14,Fwith hypertrophic cardiomyopathy, a
OL,15,Fgenetic heart disease, which can often
OL,16,Fleave her feeling breathless and tired.
OL,18,FRenee was just 31 when her mother
OL,19,FMarie died at age 49 of the same
OL,20,Fdisease.
