OL,6,FShe herself, now 72 years old, was
OL,7,Fdiagnosed in 2018 at a Nottingham
OL,8,Fhospital.
OL,10,FSince 2020, she has had two further
OL,11,Fhospital admissions where her heart
OL,12,Fwas struggling to pump blood around
OL,13,Fher body.
OL,15,FRenee, who sees a cardiologist every
OL,16,Fyear, knows her heart failure will not
OL,17,Fimprove, " But I won't slow down", she
OL,18,Fsaid, "I love my art and my work and
OL,19,Fhave no wish to stop."
