OL,6,FHer catalogue of work nods to her
OL,7,Fchildhood in Africa, with images of
OL,8,Fzebras featuring.
OL,10,FThe silent auction, which is available
OL,11,Fonline, ends at 4pm on March 1st.
OL,12,FBidding for larger canvases starting
OL,13,Fat #99, a fraction of what they
OL,14,Fusually sell for in galleries. The
OL,15,Fpaintings are available to be viewed
OL,16,Fonline, as well as in person at
OL,17,FMascari Design in Ruddington on the
OL,18,Fsame date.
