OL,6,FRenee said " Thanks to the work of the
OL,7,FBritish Heart Foundation and the
OL,8,Fmedical research, I'm on medication
OL,9,Fand I'm alive. I would love it if
OL,10,Fresearchers would come up with a new
OL,11,Fdrug that would cure me, and others,
OL,12,Fof heart failure. This is why raising
OL,13,Ffunds is so important."
