OL,6,FMel Meik, Fundraising Manager for the
OL,7,FBritish Heart Foundation said; "What
OL,8,FRenee is doing in being able to offer
OL,9,Fpeople the opportunity to buy a one-
OL,10,Foff beautiful piece of artwork and
OL,11,Fsupport life-saving and life-changing
OL,12,Fresearch for the British Heart
OL,13,FFoundation is really special."
